{
  "texts": [
    "The tasks are typically small and logical subtasks that demand less analysis and more straightforward coding, often perceived as just tedious work.",
    "Thus, to harness the acceleration potential of the AI models in coding, it is essential to first analyze and decompose the complex task into smaller logical subtasks.",
    "The exploration mode emerges when programmers encounter a new problem and are uncertain about how to decompose the task.",
    "As the tool can take code comments which is a natural text describing programming intent to generate suggestions, programmers to craft various code comments as inputs and then explore multiple implementation suggestions.",
    "Even if the suggestions are not entirely correct, they may still provide a code skeleton or starting point [142]."
  ]
}